s%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcv224kdxwm4o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcv224kdxwm4o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20To%20Stake%20Claim%20To%20Form%20Government%20After%20NDA%20Meeting%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20will%20meet%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20later%20today%20-%20'immediately'%20after%20a%20huddle%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpm-modi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E's%20residence%20to%20review%20the%20election%20result%20-%20to%20stake%20claim%20to%20form%20the%20new%20government%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20show%20of%20strength%20made%20significant%20by%20the%20underwhelming%20margin%20of%20the%20BJP's%20victory%2C%20the%20meeting%20with%20Ms%20Murmu%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20the%20party's%20senior-most%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20of%20course%2C%20includes%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20who%20is%20set%20for%20a%20historic%20third%20term%20as%20PM%2C%20and%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20his%20right-hand%20man%20and%20the%20outgoing%20Home%20Minister%2C%20as%20also%20party%20boss%20JP%20Nadda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20also%20include%20TDP%20boss%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal's%20Nitish%20Kumar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu's%20TDP%20won%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(and%20a%20simultaneous%20Assembly%20election%20to%20return%20as%20Chief%20Minister)%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%20picked%20up%2016%20seats%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%2028%20MPs%20are%20widely%20seen%20as%20propping%20up%20Mr%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20form%20a%20third%20successive%20union%20government%2C%20or%20risk%20conceding%20ground%20to%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20well-aware%20of%20their%20importance%20to%20the%20NDA%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20made%20special%20mention%20to%20the%20TDP%20and%20JDU%20bosses%20during%20his%20victory%20speech%20Tuesday%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20amid%20persistent%20speculation%20the%20two%20could%20be%20poached%20by%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20(which%20the%20Bihar%20leader%20helped%20found)%2C%20the%20optics%20of%20PM%20Modi%20flanked%20by%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20he%20submits%20his%20government%20formation%20bid%20would%20be%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20said%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20-%20veteran%20leaders%20well-versed%20in%20the%20art%20of%20coalition%20politics%20-%20could%20be%20courted%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20stake%20claim%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20has%20revealed%20their%20hand%20so%20far%2C%20but%20sources%20have%20said%20a%20variety%20of%20'demands'%2C%20including%20special%20status%20for%20their%20states%20and%20a%20pick%20of%20ministerial%20berths%20are%20on%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20defied%20exit%20pollsters%20to%20mount%20a%20real%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%20national%20election%20-%20a%20first%20since%20the%20'Modi%20wave'%20swept%20it%20to%20power%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20alliance%20finished%20with%20232%20seats%20-%2040%20short%20of%20the%20272-majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20leaders%2C%20including%20Congress%20boss%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20have%20been%20coy%20about%20reaching%20out%20to%20either%20Mr%20Naidu%20or%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20but%20the%20intent%20is%20there%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20produced%20its%20best%20performance%20since%202009%20to%20win%2099%20seats.%20In%202019%20the%20party%20won%20only%2052%20seats%20(and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20quit%20as%20boss)%2C%20while%20it%20managed%20just%2044%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20hours%20earlier%20Mr%20Modi%20met%20Ms%20Murmu%20to%20resign%20ahead%20of%20the%20dissolution%20of%20this%20government%20on%20June%2016.%20Mr%20Modi%20was%20asked%20to%20continue%20till%20a%20new%20government%20is%20appointed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20he%20chaired%20the%20final%20cabinet%20meet%20of%20his%20second%20term%2C%20and%20downplayed%20any%20raised%20eyebrows%20over%20his%20party's%20performance%3B%20%26quot%3BWinning%20and%20losing%20are%20part%20of%20politics...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20done%20good%20work%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20We%20will%20continue%20doing%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717587300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fjhr2m54g_nda-meeting_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-stake-claim-to-form-government-after-nda-meeting-today-5823912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20will%20meet%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20later%20today%20-%20'immediately'%20after%20a%20huddle%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20residence%20to%20review%20the%20election%20result%20-%20to%20stake%20claim%20to%20form%20the%20government%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-stake-claim-to-form-government-after-nda-meeting-today-5823912%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-stake-claim-to-form-government-after-nda-meeting-today-5823912%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22htt