r%20Naidu%20--%20erstwhile%20allies%20who%20are%20now%20part%20of%20the%20NDA.%20Neither%20leader%20is%20known%20to%20be%20rigid.%20In%20fact%2C%20both%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20Opposition%20earlier.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Kumar%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20Opposition%20even%20four%20months%20ago%20and%20was%20responsible%20for%20starting%20the%20initiative%20for%20a%20cohesive%20opposition%20bloc.%20But%20he%20changed%20sides%20--%20again%20--%20upset%20over%20the%20leadership%20issue.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Naidu%2C%20who%20quit%20NDA%20and%20became%20part%20of%20the%20Opposition%20ahead%20of%20the%20last%20general%20election%2C%20took%20a%20U-turn%20in%20February%20this%20year%20as%20the%20BJP%20started%20patching%20up%20with%20erstwhile%20allies%20and%20looking%20for%20new%20ones.%20Earlier%20today%2C%20while%20walking%20into%20the%20NDA%20meeting%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%20he%20was%20with%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20has%20responded%20with%20a%20jab.%20On%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20he%20posted%20a%20video%20where%20Mr%20Naidu%20is%20heard%20criticising%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BAll%20leaders%20are%20better%20than%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20is%20heard%20saying%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20240%20seats%20and%20293%20with%20its%20allies%20--%2028%20of%20them%20are%20contributions%20of%20Mr%20Kumar%20and%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Chief%20Minister-elect%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20with%20a%20spectacular%20comeback%20under%20his%20belt.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20232%20seats%2C%2099%20from%20Congress%20alone.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717587120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fporrp61_narendra-modi_625x300_05_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-nda-tries-to-close-deal-india-bloc-to-brainstorm-strategy-5823869%22%