%20four%20group%20matches%20will%20also%20be%20held%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20match%20against%20Ireland%2C%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20isn't%20sure%20which%20pitch%20would%20be%20used%20for%20their%20game%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20square%20of%20four%20pitches.%20I%20don't%20know%20which%20wicket%20we%20will%20be%20playing%20on.%20So%2C%20who%20knows%20-%20the%20wicket%20that%20we%20are%20playing%20tomorrow%20might%20be%20a%20good%20wicket%20to%20bat%20on.%20So%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20adapting%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20in%20a%20pre-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20added%20that%20while%20he%20didn't%20watch%20the%20match%20between%20South%20Africa%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20Indian%20players%20will%20do%20their%20best%20to%20adapt%20if%20the%20conditions%20are%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20get%20to%20watch%20the%20game.%20I%20was%20a%20little%20busy%20with%20my%20family%20who%20had%20arrived%20yesterday.%20But%20no%2C%20certainly%20I%20know%20how%20the%20pitch%20played%2C%20hearing%20from%20my%20other%20teammates%2C%20and%20we've%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20guys%20in%20the%20team%20and%20the%20support%20staff%20were%20talking%20about%20what%20happened%20in%20that%20game.%20But%2C%20again%2C%20all%20I%20can%20say%20is%20we'll%20make%20the%20best%20decision%20possible%20for%20these%20conditions%2C%20whatever%20the%20best%20level%20we%20feel.%20We'll%20just%20go%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20have%20a%20look%20at%20the%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20also%20signed%20off%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20outfield%20at%20the%20newly-built%20stadium%20is%20also%20a%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertainly%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20are%20very%20uncertain