s%20Party%20(YSRCP)%2C%20the%20Sikkim%20Democratic%20Front%20(SDF)%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20and%20a%20few%20others%2C%20good%20fortune%20favoured%20most%20others%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoalition%20Dharma%20Again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talk%20of%20a%20'Congress-%3Cem%3Emukt%20%3C%2Fem%3EBharat'%2C%20which%20had%20been%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20since%20it%20ousted%20the%20former%20in%202014%2C%20is%20now%20moot%20given%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-results-rahul-gandhi-priyanka-gandhi-vadra-mocked-by-bjp-for-years-gandhi-siblings-shine-in-indias-stellar-show-5815870%5C%22%3Ehow%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20pulled%20his%20party%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20depths%20of%20irrelevance%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-proud-to-be-your-sister-priyanka-gandhis-post-for-rahul-after-results-5822260%5C%22%3Ealmost%20doubled%20its%20seat%20share%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Though%20its%20tally%20of%2099%20did%20not%20touch%20the%20three-digit%20mark%20-%20a%20distinction%20claimed%20by%20the%20BJP%20alone%20since%202014%20-%20the%20Congress's%20performance%20can%20still%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP's%20pan-India%20dominance%20has%20been%20reaffirmed%20again.%20Falling%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20by%2032%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20eyeing%20a%20third%20term%20as%20the%20ruling%20party.%20Its%20tally%20of%20240%20surpasses%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20combined%20seat%20share%20of%20234.%20The%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20won%20291%20seats%2C%20which%20provides%20it%20with%20a%20clear%20mandate%20for%20forming%20the%20government.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20a%20way%2C%20the%20decade-long%20single-party%20dominance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20now%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20coalition%20-%20the%20norm%20in%20Indian%20politics%20between%201991%20and%202014.%20Modi's%20hat-trick%20thus%20does%20not%20equal%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20unencumbered%20three%20wins%20between%201952%20and%201962.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-results-rahul-gandhis-hat-tip-to-priyanka-for-india-blocs-impressive-up-show-5816677%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Hat%20Tip%20To%20Priyanka%20For%20INDIA%20Bloc's%20Impressive%20UP%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaking%20Cue%20From%20Vajpayee%20Era%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20himself%2C%20who%20has%20seen%20unfettered%20power%20since%202001%2C%20first%20as%20Gujarat's%20Chief%20Minister%20till%202014%20and%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20after%20that%2C%20will%20have%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20paradigm%20of%20'coalition%20dharma'%20now.%20In%201998%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20of%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20made%20Atal%20Behari%20Vajpayee%20yield%20the%20post%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker.%20Apart%20from%20him%2C%20the%20BJP's%20other%20major%20ally%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)'s%20(JD-U)%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20is%20also%20known%20to%20be%20a%20hard%20bargainer.%20Both%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20had%20been%20Modi's%20contemporaries%20in%20their%20respective%20states%20when%20he%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20in%20Gujarat.%20Today%2C%20the%20two%20have%20emerged%20as%20kingmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20now%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20would%20try%20to%20wean%20away%20the%20BJP's%20allies.%20But%20given%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish's%20past%20experience%20with%20INDIA%2C%20that%20may%20not%20be%20easy.%20A%20lot%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20BJP's%20coalition%20management%2C%20and%20in%20that%2C%20a%20leaf%20from%20the%20Vajpayee%20era%20may%20be%20of%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-result-how-everyone-failed-to-read-the-tea-leaves-against-bjp-in-uttar-pradesh-5818762%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20How%20Almost%20Everyone%20Missed%20The%20All-Too-Visible%20Signs%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20opposition%2C%20this%20marks%20a%20big%20resurgence%20with%20the%20Congress%20having%20reversed%20the%20bad%20luck%20of%20the%20last%20two%20elections.%20With%2099%20seats%2C%20its%20floor%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20now%20be%20recognised%20as%20a%20legitimate%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20(a%20party%20needs%2010%25%20seats%20to%20be%20so%20recognised%2C%20but%2044%20seats%20in%202014%20and%2052%20in%202019%20deprived%20the%20Congress%20of%20this%20privilege).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Rigging'%20Claims%20Fall%20Silent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20allegations%20of%20'rigging'%20and%20the%20aspersions%20cast%20on%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20seem%20to%20have%20faded%20into%20obscurity.%20On%20January%2025%2C%20when%20asked%20by%20this%20writer%20how%20the%20Congress%20could%20possibly%20have%20won%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20if%20the%20EVMs%20were%20indeed%20rigged%2C%20Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20the%20Congress's%20overseas%20chief%20and%20a%20tech%20czar%20according%20to%20many%2C%20had%20patronisingly%20brushed%20the%20query%20aside.%20Petitions%20were%20moved%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20questioning%20the%20credibility%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20(Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail).%20The%20apex%20court%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20indulge%20the%20petitioners%2C%20who%20among%20other%20things%20advocated%20going%20back%20to%20paper%20ballots%2C%20citing%20examples%20from%20abroad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20post-poll%20meeting%20convened%20by%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20on%20June%201%20did%20not%20discuss%20an%20alternate%20plan%20of%20governance%2C%20even%20as%20the%20participants%20exuded%20confidence%20that%20Modi%20would%20be%20defeated.%20Instead%2C%20they%20asked%20the%20ECI%20to%20count%20the%20postal%20ballots%20before%20opening%20the%20EVMs%2C%20which%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20quickly%20pointed%20out%2C%20was%20already%20the%20norm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20appeals%20rebuffed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-andhra-pradesh-mla-p-ramakrishan-reddy-smashed-evm-bail-this-is-a-joke-top-court-furious-over-bail-for-andhra-mla-who-smashed-evm-5806728%5C%22%3Eapex%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Opposition%20then%20made%20a%20last-minute%20attempt%20to%20discredit%20the%20world's%20largest-functioning%20election%20machinery%2C%20which%20since%201952%20has%20acted%20as%20a%20beacon%20for%20electoral%20management%20the%20world%20over.%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20alleged%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20counting%20that%20officials%20in%20seven%20states%20had%20been%20'pressured'%20by%20the%20ruling%20regime.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20was%20alleged%20to%20have%20telephoned%20'150%20District%20Magistrates'%20to%20instruct%20them%20about%20'managing'%20the%20poll%20verdict.%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%2C%20taking%20immediate%20cognisance%2C%20asked%20Ramesh%20to%20furnish%20details%20on%20June%203%20itself%2C%20so%20that%20corrective%20action%20could%20be%20taken%20before%20counting%20began.%20But%20Ramesh%20sought%20a%20week's%20time%20to%20furnish%20these%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20on%20June%204%20disproved%20all%20the%20naysaying.%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20got%20a%20fair%20share%20of%20the%20booty.%20While%20the%20BJP%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20it%20won%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Odisha%20with%20its%20allies.%20In%20Odisha%2C%20the%2025-year%20hegemony%20of%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20drew%20to%20an%20end.%20The%20Congress%20drew%20a%20blank%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Sikkim%2C%20finished%20third%20with%20merely%2010%25%20of%20seats%20in%20Odisha%2C%20and%20won%20a%20single%20seat%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20(where%20it%20anyway%20had%20not%20fielded%20candidates%20for%2041%20of%20the%2060%20seats).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpset%20In%20UP%2C%20Continuity%20In%20Bengal%2C%20And%20New%20Wins%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20(SP)%20resurgence%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20it%20won%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20BJP%2C%20was%20remarkable.%20The%20Congress%20rode%20on%20its%20coattails%20and%20won%20six%20seats%20(the%20party%20has%20just%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20assembly).%20The%20SP's%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20harped%20on%20his%3Cem%3E%20Pichhda-Dalit-Alpsankhyak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20the%20PDA%2C%20formula%3B%20INDIA%20was%20rarely%20referred%20to.%20In%20neighbouring%20Bihar%2C%20though%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal's%20(RJD)%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20emerged%20as%20an%20energetic%20campaigner%2C%20his%20party%20could%20not%20benefit%20from%20its%20INDIA%20bloc%20membership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20held%20its%20ground%2C%20while%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20in%20Maharashtra%20have%20registered%20a%20sound%20resurrection%20after%20seeing%20deep%20splits%20and%20losing%20their%20symbols%20to%20rebel%20factions%3A%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truncated%20tally%20of%20the%20BJP%20can%20also%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20erosion%20of%20its%20relations%20with%20erstwhile%20allies%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20SAD.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20sidelining%20of%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20may%20have%20enabled%20the%20Congress%20to%20stall%20the%20BJP's%20sweep.%20The%20BJP%20must%20thus%20introspect%20on%20its%20inter-%20and%20intra-party%20management%20as%20it%20reviews%20the%202024%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%20though%2C%20by%20winning%20a%20seat%20in%20Kerala%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20expanded%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20South.%20This%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20victory%20in%20Odisha%2C%20pushes%20the%20party's%20pan-India%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP's%20loss%20in%20Faizabad%20-%20of%20which%20Ayodhya%20is%20a%20part%20-%20and%20the%20scraping%20win%20in%20Meerut%20of%20the%20telly%20%26quot%3BRam%26quot%3B%2C%20Arun%20Govil%2C%20point%20to%20a%20possible%20waning%20of%20Hindutva's%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestions%20Around%20Three%20Independents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResults%20in%20three%20seats%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20are%20also%20of%20concern.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20rejoices%20in%20his%20party's%20upsurge%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassin%2C%20Sarabjit%20Khalsa%2C%20has%20been%20elected%20as%20an%20Independent%20from%20the%20Congress-dominated%20Faridkot%20seat%20in%20Punjab.%20Another%20Punjab%20seat%2C%20Khadoor%20Sahab%2C%20has%20returned%20Amritpal%20Singh%20as%20the%20winner%3B%20he%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20Assam's%20Dibrugarh%20for%20his%20separatist%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir's%20Baramulla%2C%20Abdul%20Rasheed%2C%20better%20known%20as%20'Engineer%20Rasheed'%20and%20currently%20in%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20jail%20over%20terrorism%20funding%20charges%2C%20has%20defeated%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20as%20well%20as%20Sajjad%20Lone%2C%20son%20of%20yet%20another%20Kashmir%20stalwart.%20The%20unprecedentedly%20high%20voter%20turnout%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20is%20a%20good%20indicator.%20But%20the%20victories%20of%20these%20three%20Independents%20in%20sensitive%20border%20states%20do%20not%20bode%20well%20for%20India's%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717583700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fd64a3i1_pm-modi_625x300_04_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F2024-verdict-settles-some-questions-but-it-also-raises-others-5823519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20talk%20of%20a%20'Congress-mukt%20Bharat'%2C%20which%20had%20been%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20since%20it%20ousted%20the%20former%20in%202014%2C%20is%20now%20moot.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP's%20pan-India%20dominance%20has%20been%20reaffirmed%20again.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F2024-verdict-settles-some-questions-but-it-also-raises-others-5823519%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suhana%20Khan%20stuns%20in%20summer%20dress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717583400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110712250%2Cimgsize-106052.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fsuhana-khan-stuns-in-summer-dress-for-anant-amp-radhikas-pre-wedding-celebrations-in-italy%2Fphotostory%2F110712250.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110712250.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESuhana%20Khan%20stun