%20Coachella%20lagged%20this%20year%2C%20and%20there's%20been%20chatter%20about%20a%20variety%20of%20acts%20not%20hitting%20home%20runs%20sales-wise%2C%20including%20Cardi%20B%2C%20Justin%20Timberlake%2C%20and%20Pink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20entire%20concert%20industry%20is%20in%20disarray.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhow-to-buy-taylor-swift-tour-tickets-concert-prices-compared%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%20is%20unstoppable%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeyonce-renaissance-tour-listening-only-no-view-tickets-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeyonc%C3%A9%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhenever%20she%20is%20on%20the%20road.%20Acts%20such%20as%20Luke%20Combs%2C%20Zach%20Bryan%2C%20and%20Olivia%20Rodrigo%20are%20selling%20a%20ton.%20Dead%20%26amp%3B%20Company%2C%20the%20successor%20band%20to%20the%20Grateful%20Dead%2C%20is%20adding%20dates%20at%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Sphere.%20Live%20Nation%2C%20which%20owns%20Ticketmaster%20and%20rules%20the%20roost%20in%20the%20live-events%20space%2C%20had%20a%20huge%202023%2C%20estimating%20that%20145%20million%20fans%20attended%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20events%2C%20a%2020%25%20increase%20in%20fans%20over%20the%20year%20before.%20However%2C%20not%20everything%20is%20going%20smoothly%20for%20everyone.%20For%20some%20artists%2C%20conditions%20aren't%20so%20favorable%2C%20and%20they're%20struggling%20to%20pull%20in%20the%20crowds%20they%20anticipated%2C%20at%20least%20right%20out%20of%20the%20gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConcert%20promotion%20is%20a%20betting%20business.%20You%20don't%20always%20win.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20you%20can%20be%20humbled%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jarred%20Arfa%2C%20the%20head%20of%20global%20music%20at%20Independent%20Artist%20Group%2C%20whose%20client%20roster%20includes%20Billy%20Joel%2C%2050%20Cent%2C%20and%20Metallica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%20that%20are%20dragging%20down%20some%20artists'%20ticket%20sales.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20%3Cem%3Ea%20lot%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20acts%20are%20on%20tour%20at%20the%20moment.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20artists%20have%20been%20eager%20to%20get%20back%20out%20there%20and%20recoup%20lost%20time%20and%20money.%20Even%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusicians-make-money-touring-taylor-swift-tickets-ticketmaster-live-nation-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20return%20hasn't%20been%20smooth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20basically%20anyone%20who%20can%20be%20touring%20is%2C%20meaning%20the%20space%20is%20crowded%20and%20oversaturated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'd%20never%20before%20had%20a%20moment%20in%20time%20where%20all%20the%20horses%20lined%20up%20at%20the%20starting%20gate%20and%20they%20all%20went%20out%20on%20the%20road%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gary%20Witt%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20co-owner%20of%20The%20Pabst%20Theater%20Group%20in%20Milwaukee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20really%20is%20your%20oyster%20right%20now%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20catching%20a%20show.%20But%20it%20also%20means%20that%20people%20have%20a%20ton%20of%20options%2C%20and%20there%20is%20only%20so%20much%20time%20to%20go%20around.%20Maybe%20you%20already%20saw%20your%20favorite%20artist%20when%20they%20first%20went%20on%20the%20road%20after%20the%20worst%20of%20COVID%20passed%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20feel%20especially%20inspired%20to%20go%20see%20them%20again.%20Or%20you%20like%20the%20band%20or%20singer%20in%20question%20plenty%2C%20but%20not%20enough%20to%20go%20through%20all%20the%20rigamarole%20of%20seeing%20them%20live.%20Either%20way%2C%20the%20once%20feverish%20demand%20for%20that%20ticket%20has%20probably%20cooled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPricing%20is%20also%20a%20factor.%20Anyone%20who's%20looked%20for%20concert%20tickets%20recently%20has%20probably%20been%20gobsmacked%20at%20the%20cost.%20Many%20consumers%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhate-spending-consumers-economic-sentiment-retail-sales-inflation-gdp-growth-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20through%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20if%20begrudgingly%20so%2C%20but%20no%20one's%20budget%20is%20limitless%2C%20especially%20as%20prices%20for%20basically%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20including%20tickets%20to%20live%20events%20%E2%80%94%20remain%20elevated.%20Pollstar%20calculated%20that%20the%20average%20ticket%20price%20for%20the%20top%20100%20tours%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%20was%20%24123.25%2C%20an%20all-time.%20Its%20data%20indicates%20that%20the%20average%20ticket%20price%20for%20a%20Bad%20Bunny%20ticket%20is%20%24290%2C%20for%20Justin%20Timberlake%20%24216%2C%20and%20for%20Nicki%20Minaj%20%24149.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTicket%20prices%20are%20just%20astronomical%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20%26quot%3B5-1%26quot%3B%20Norman%2C%20an%20industry%20veteran%20who%20has%20toured%20with%20Prince%2C%20Green%20Day%2C%20and%20Alicia%20Keys.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you're%20bringing%20a%20child%20with%20you%2C%20and%20then%20you%20have%20to%20stay%20overnight%20and%20gas%20and%20hotel%20and%20then%20food%2C%20that%20stuff%20adds%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20on%20tour%20is%20always%20a%20gamble%20based%20on%20numerous%20factors%20including%20ticket%20history%2C%20streaming%20performance%2C%20email%20list%20sizes%2C%20and%20online%20attention.%20But%20there%20are%20no%20guarantees%20that%20any%20of%20that%20will%20translate%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-reselling-tickets-earns-me-tens-of-thousands-per-month-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehard%20ticket%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20are%20artists%20who%20might%20have%20massive%20numbers%20online%20but%20whose%20fans%20are%20only%20surface-level%20and%20don't%20really%20care%20enough%20to%20appear%20at%20a%20show.%20The%20way%20artists%20break%20out%20on%20social%20media%20nowadays%20makes%20it%20even%20harder%20to%20figure%20out%20whether%20that%20might%20be%20the%20case.%20Having%20a%20couple%20of%20hits%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-streaming-music-brutal-business-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotify%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-is-changing-music-industry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20mean%20someone%20can%20sell%20out%20a%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20degree%20of%20overshooting.%20Artists%20(and%20their%20agents%20and%20managers%20and%20promoters)%20are%20trying%20to%20sell%20out%20bigger%20venues%20than%20they%20can.%20A%20more%20conservative%20approach%20would%20be%20to%20book%20a%20handful%20of%20big%20venues%20and%20see%20how%20it%20goes%20before%20committing%20to%20more%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20approach%20everyone%20is%20taking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20some%20hard-rock%20artists%20who%20you've%20never%20even%20heard%20of%20and%20they%20sell%20out%20everywhere%2C%20but%20they%20have%20that%20loyal%20fan%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20Arfa%20said.%20%26quot%3BJust%20having%20the%20big%20song%20doesn't%20necessarily%20always%20translate%20into%20ticket%20sales.%26quot%3B%20For%20every%20five%20or%20six%20acts%20that%20are%20doing%20great%20touring%2C%20one%20is%20a%20little%20clunky%2C%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20having%20a%20couple%20conversations%20where%20we're%20thinking%20it%20may%20be%20best%20to%20push%20into%20Q1%20of%20next%20year%20because%20of%20a%20high%20level%20of%20traffic%20on%20the%20road%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20artist%20and%20situation%20is%20unique.%20Bad%20Bunny%20may%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20sell%20such%20high-priced%20tickets%20in%20Minneapolis%2C%20but%20he's%20sold%20a%20ton%20of%20other%20places.%20JLo%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20on%20her%20plate%20than%20trying%20to%20tour%20right%20now%2C%20and%20the%20Black%20Keys%20will%20probably%20do%20fine%20in%20smaller%20venues.%20A%20representative%20for%20Live%20Nation%2C%20which%20is%20producing%20the%20Troye%20Sivan%2FCharli%20XCX%20show%2C%20said%20the%20tour%20had%20sold%20out%20some%20dates%20and%20was%2070%25%20sold%20across%20the%20board%2C%20implying%20there%20had%20been%20misconceptions%20about%20sales%20online.%20(They%20said%20Wallows%20is%20selling%20%26quot%3Bwell%26quot%3B%20without%20providing%20on-the-record%20specifics%20and%20pointed%20to%20public%20statements%20from%20the%20Black%20Keys%20and%20Lopez%2C%20the%20tours%20of%20which%20Live%20Nation%20all%20produced.)%20Hiccups%20are%20not%20all%20about%20ticket%20sales%2C%20either.%20Kid%20Cudi%20canceled%20his%20tour%20this%20year%20because%20he%20broke%20his%20foot%20jumping%20off%20the%20stage%20during%20Coachella%2C%20and%20many%20acts%20aren't%20specifically%20saying%20the%20problem%20is%20sales%20when%20they%20do%20cancel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20strategies%20acts%20undertake%20to%20try%20to%20freshen%20things%20up%20for%20fans%20and%20boost%20sales%2C%20such%20as%20combining%20forces%20or%20bringing%20in%20special%20guests.%20Def%20Leppard%20is%20touring%20with%20Journey%20this%20year%2C%20and%20last%20year%20it%20toured%20with%20M%C3%B6tley%20Cr%C3%BCe.%20There's%20always%20good%20old%20marketing.%20Live%20Nation%20recently%20wrapped%20its%20%26quot%3Bconcert%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20offers%20a%20variety%20of%20tickets%20at%20%2425%20%E2%80%94%20a%20good%20way%20to%20push%20tickets%20that%20aren't%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20a%20huge%20issue%20that%20undergirds%20the%20entire%20conversation%3A%20Buying%20tickets%20is%20supremely%20annoying.%20You%20have%20to%20really%20want%20to%20see%20a%20show%20to%20try%20to%20navigate%20the%20labyrinthine%20purchase%20process.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fticketmaster-arena-ampitheater-monopoly-transparent-pricing-worthless-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELive%20Nation-Ticketmaster%20dominates%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20market%2C%20which%20critics%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-ticketmaster-fiasco-doj-lawsuit-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20is%20suing%20the%20company%20over%20claims%20of%20anti-competitive%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20say%20stifles%20innovation%2C%20allows%20for%20unfair%20markups%2C%20and%20contributes%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fticketmaster-under-fire-faces-fine-selling-fake-bad-bunny-tickets-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverall%20negative%20experience%20for%20fans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fees%20on%20tickets%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-businesses-add-90-billion-junk-fees-each-year-backfiring-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfoundingly%20high%20and%20seemingly%20endless%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bot%20armies%20snatch%20up%20tickets%20when%20they%20go%20on%20sale%20and%20flip%20them%20on%20the%20secondary%20markets%20for%20exorbitantly%20high%20prices.%20(One%20piece%20of%20silver%20lining%20here%20is%20that%20this%20year's%20lowered%20demand%20has%20resulted%20in%20lower%20resale%20ticket%20prices.%20SeatGeek%20says%20the%20average%20resale%20ticket%20price%20to%20attend%20a%20summer%20concert%20this%20year%20is%20%24214%3B%20last%20year%2C%20it%20was%20%24257%2C%20though%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20was%20due%20to%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20time%20when%20customer%20experiences%20aren't%20good%20is%20usually%20when%20there's%20a%20monopoly%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Witt%2C%20from%20The%20Pabst%20Theater%20Group%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLo%2C%20of%20course%2C%20will%