%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELi%20Auto's%20electric%20minivan%20was%20displayed%20at%20a%20trade%20show.%3Cp%3EVCG%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELi%20Auto%20workers%20are%20facing%20layoffs%20or%20minimum%20wage%20due%20to%20weak%20electric%20vehicle%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20auto%20sector%20is%20struggling%20with%20overproduction%2C%20impacting%20domestic%20and%20international%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWestern%20concerns%20over%20subsidies%20and%20overcapacity%20add%20pressure%20as%20Chinese%20EV%20makers%20seek%20new%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20China%20grapples%20with%20manufacturing%20overproduction%2C%20some%20workers%20at%20one%20of%20China's%20auto%20plants%20face%20a%20difficult%20choice%20about%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewlywed%20Lisa%20told%20Nikkei%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20in%20her%20brand-new%20factory%20for%20Li%20Auto%2C%20more%20than%201%2C000%20employees%20like%20her%20were%20given%20the%20choice%20of%20either%20quitting%20or%20receiving%20minimum%20wage%20until%20business%20improves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20told%20that%20our%20pure%20electric%20vehicle%20sales%20are%20weak%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20conditions%2C%20so%20the%20company%20has%20to%20cut%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2027-year-old%20Lisa%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20Nikkei.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20try%20to%20find%20a%20job.%20Otherwise%2C%20I%20will%20be%20starving%20to%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20reported%20last%20month%20that%20Li%20Auto%20was%20planning%20to%20cut%2018%25%20of%20its%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi%20Auto%20delivered%2080%2C400%20cars%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20the%20year%2C%20up%2053%25%20from%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20but%20down%2039%25%20from%20the%20last%20quarter%20of%202023%2C%20per%20its%20financial%20results.%20The%20company%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%2C%20by%20comparison%2C%20delivered%20386%2C810%20cars%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20%E2%80%94%20down%208.5%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20and%2020%25%20from%20the%20prior%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi%20Auto's%20financials%20are%20emblematic%20of%20the%20arc%20of%20China's%20electric%20vehicle%20industry.%20Car%20makers%20scaled%20up%20production%20quickly%20but%20have%20struggled%20to%20drum%20up%20enough%20demand%20for%20all%20their%20cars%2C%20especially%20as%20domestic%20consumers%20face%20a%20real%20estate%20crisis%20and%20volatile%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20automakers%20are%20looking%20to%20other%20countries%20as%20bigger%20markets%2C%20but%20politicians%20seeking%20to%20protect%20local%20manufacturers%20are%20cutting%20China%20off.%20Last%20month%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20it%20would%20impose%20a%20100%25%20tax%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-joe-biden-hikes-tariffs-on-chinese-made-evs-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese-made%20EVs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYao%20Xiaodong%2C%20an%20official%20for%20a%20Chinese%20EV%20group%2C%20said%20at%20a%20recent%20meeting%20that%20manufacturers%20could%20%26quot%3Beither%20go%20overseas%20or%20go%20bust%2C%26quot%3B%20Nikkei%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20leaders%20have%20publicly%20said%20that%20the%20West's%20focus%20on%20supposed%20overproduction%20is%20election-year%20posturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Western%20investors%20and%20politicians%20have%20been%20raising%20red%20flags%20about%20overcapacity%20for%20years%2C%20saying%20the%20Chinese%20government's%20huge%20manufacturing%20subsidies%20have%20led%20to%20cheap%20goods%20that%20distort%20the%20global%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20is%20now%20simply%20too%20large%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20to%20absorb%20this%20enormous%20capacity%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Janet%20Yellen%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20primarily%20concerned%20about%20factory%20underutilization%20and%20competition%20leading%20to%20too%20many%20unprofitable%20companies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-overcapacity-us-concerns-green-overproduction-different-yellen-ev-solar-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20reported%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderutilization%20or%20closures%20of%20factories%20like%20Lisa's%20means%20less%20tax%20revenue%20for%20regional%20governments%20who%20have%20often%20borrowed%20significant%20sums%20for%20local%20development%2C%20fewer%20materials%20purchased%20from%20other%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20and%20an%20unemployed%20or%20underemployed%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautoworkers-quit-make-minimum-wage-china-overproduction-manufacturing-electric-vehicles-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717580842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660256ccc442a2f676e0a03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautoworkers-quit-make-minimum-wage-china-overproduction-manufacturing-electric-vehicles-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20auto%20sector%20is%20struggling%20with%20overproduction%2C%20impacting%20domestic%20and%20international%20markets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Meghan%20Morris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautoworkers-quit-make-minimum-wage-china-overproduction-manufacturing-electric-vehicles-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BTS%20to%20host%20free%20livestream%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717580760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h