%2F2c4h1tuo_pm-modi_625x300_01_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20voted%20yet%20again%20for%20her%20favourite%20son%2C%20for%20its%20most%20loved%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20modern%20post-independence%20history.%20When%20a%20democracy%20as%20large%2C%20complex%20and%20varied%20as%20India%20chooses%20a%20leader%20for%20a%20third%20time%2C%20it%20simply%20means%20that%20the%20country%20enjoys%20a%20very%20special%20relationship%20with%20this%20leader.%20A%20relationship%20based%20on%20belief%20and%20trust%20-%20unparalleled%20in%20Indian%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20no%20mistake%20-%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20won%20a%20historic%20mandate.%20This%20is%20the%20third%20general%20election%20won%20under%20his%20leadership%20by%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%20Many%20historic%20facts%20for%20democracy%20in%20general%20and%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20been%20rewritten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPart%20of%20an%20Elite%20Group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVery%20few%20leaders%20in%20modern%20democracies%20have%20won%20three%20mandates.%20In%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20wartime%20President%2C%20Franklin%20D.%20Roosevelt%2C%20and%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Margaret%20Thatcher%2C%20won%20three%20terms.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20outdone%20the%20most%20popular%20global%20leaders%20today%2C%20despite%20having%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20during%20a%20black%20swan%20event%2C%20the%20devastating%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMassive%2C%20Mindboggling%20Scale%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi's%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20won%20236%20million%20votes%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20elections.%20This%20number%20is%20not%20too%20different%20from%20the%20combined%20number%20of%20votes%20polled%20by%20the%20winning%20candidate%20in%20the%20last%20three%20US%20Presidential%20elections%2C%20the%20winning%20party%20in%20the%20last%20UK%20general%20election%20and%20the%20winning%20candidates%20in%20the%20last%20European%20Parliament%20-%20put%20together!%3Cbr%3E%5CnOf%20course%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20already%20set%20the%20bar%20high.%20He%20had%20secured%20171%20million%20votes%20in%202014%20and%20229%20million%20votes%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20is%20the%20only%20other%20Prime%20Minister%20after%20Jawahar%20Lal%20Nehru%20to%20have%20won%20three%20consecutive%20terms.%20Nehru%2C%20of%20course%2C%20won%20elections%20soon%20after%20the%20British%20era%20was%20over%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20enjoyed%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%20dividend%26quot%3B%20-%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20political%20agent%20facilitating%20independence.%20In%20that%20era%2C%20the%20opposition%20was%20nascent%20and%20ill-equipped.%20Three%20consecutive%20terms%20in%20the%20digital%20age%20under%2024x7%20glare%20and%20scrutiny%20of%20cameras%20and%20against%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20which%20have%20had%2054%20years%20of%20ruling%20experience%2C%20stands%20out%20handsomely.%20Even%20in%20these%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20secured%20137%20million%20votes%2C%20approximately%20100%20million%20votes%20less%20than%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20alone%20has%20managed%20to%20get%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20entire%20opposition%20camp%20put%20together.%20The%20Congress%2C%20after%2010%20years%20in%20power%2C%20in%202014%2C%20was%20reduced%20to%20just%2044%20seats.%20The%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20has%20won%20240%20seats%20and%20the%20NDA%20is%20all%20set%20for%20a%20third%20term%20in%20office.%20No%20amount%20of%20chest-thumping%20by%20the%20opposition%20can%20change%20the%20simple%20undeniable%20fact%20that%20the%20public%20of%20India%20has%20once%20again%20reposed%20their%20faith%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeadership%20with%20Longevity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20defeat%20of%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20in%20Odisha%2C%20PM%20Modi%20is%20set%20to%20become%20the%20longest-serving%20head%20of%20an%20elected%20government%20in%20India.%20He%20has%20not%20seen%20an%20electoral%20defeat%20in%20a%20political%20career%20spanning%20almost%2023%20years%2C%20as%20both%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20now%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELongest%20PM%20Tenure%20Won%20In%20Own%20Name%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Nehru%20served%20a%20whole%20five%20years%20until%20independent%20India%20held%20its%20first%20general%20election%20in%201952.%20These%20five%20prime%20ministerial%20years%20were%20effectively%20gifted%20to%20him%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20He%20then%20served%2012%20years%20as%20PM%20after%201952.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20served%20two%20years%20of%20a%20term%20won%20originally%20by%20her%20father.%20She%20then%20imposed%20Emergency%20when%20she%20should%20have%20resigned%20having%20been%20held%20guilty%20of%20electoral%20malpractices%2C%20and%20served%20two%20more%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20PM%20Modi%20completes%20his%20third%20term%2C%20he%20will%20have%20served%2015%20years%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20seeking%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20Indian%20voters%20in%20his%20name%20and%20for%20his%20leadership%20track%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20record-breaking%20spree%20should%20hardly%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20PM%20Modi's%20track%20record%20has%20been%20deep%20in%20its%20meticulousness%20and%20wide%20in%20its%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStandout%20Leadership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20brought%20India%20together.%20%C2%A0He%20took%20historic%20and%20bold%20decisions%20that%20his%20predecessors%20avoided%20or%20could%20not%20deliver%20within%20the%20mandate%20they%20had.%20The%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20to%20integrate%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20tackling%20terrorism%20and%20bringing%20unprecedented%20development%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20attacking%20the%20Naxal%20problem%20and%20the%20cultural%20unification%20of%20the%20country%20through%20efforts%20such%20as%20Ek%20Bharat%20Shreshtha%20Bharat%2C%20the%20Kashi-Tamil%20Sangam%20and%20the%20symbolism%20of%20placing%20the%20Sengol%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%20are%20noteworthy.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20also%20prioritised%20India's%20security%20interests%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20be%20it%20the%20surgical%20strikes%2C%20ambitious%20defence%20deals%20or%20India's%20renewed%20thrust%20on%20defence%20preparedness%20and%20developing%20indigenous%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20differentiator%20for%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20has%20been%20his%20commitment%20to%20and%20furtherance%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BVishwa%20Mitra%26quot%3B.%20While%20cultivating%20new%20international%20relations%2C%20he%20has%20also%20fully%20maintained%20the%20old%20ones%2C%20deftly%20balancing%20what%20was%20earlier%20thought%20of%20as%20contradictions.%20He%20has%20been%20guided%20solely%20by%20the%20interest%20of%20India%2C%20using%20an%20Indian%20lens%20to%20further%20geopolitical%20relations%2C%20developing%20an%20%3Cem%3Eaatmanirbharta%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20imagination.%20Under%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%20India's%20G-20%20presidency%20showcased%20Sanatan%20culture%20proudly%20through%20hundreds%20of%20events%20and%20delegate%20engagements.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20consistently%20topped%20the%20ranking%20of%20global%20leaders%20with%20approval%20ratings%20above%2075%25%20throughout%20his%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20Delivery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20noteworthy%20global%20leaders%20such%20as%20Franklin%20D.%20Roosevelt%20of%20the%20US%2C%20Shinzo%20Abe%20of%20Japan%20and%20Lee%20Kuan%20Yew%20of%20Singapore%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20navigated%20choppy%20waters%20to%20pull%20India%20to%20the%20global%20centre-stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20chosen%20to%20lead%20India%20-%20was%20termed%20Fragile%20Five%20by%20Morgan%20Stanley%20-%20whose%20GDP%20growth%20rate%20was%20stagnant%2C%20whose%20state-run%20banks%20had%20record%20non-performing%20assets%20(NPAs)%20and%20which%20was%20rocked%20by%20one%20corruption%20scandal%20after%20another.%20To%20top%20it%2C%20he%20was%20faced%20with%20a%20once-in-a-century%20global%20pandemic%20and%20the%20resulting%20economic%20slowdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20today%2C%20India%20is%20the%20world's%20fifth-largest%20economy%2C%20on%20its%20way%20to%20becoming%20the%20third-largest.%20The%20GDP%20growth%20rate%20is%20healthy%2C%20with%20the%20most%20recent%20financial%20year%20producing%208.2%25%20growth.%20The%20state-run%20banks%20have%20recorded%20the%20lowest%20levels%20of%20NPAs%20and%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20Macro-Stability%20With%20Welfarism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiscal%20prudence%20and%20macroeconomic%20stability%20have%20been%20managed%20hand-in-hand%20with%20stellar%20welfarism%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Under%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%20250%20million%20Indians%20have%20been%20lifted%20out%20of%20poverty%2C%20an%20unprecedented%20feat%20and%20one%20that%20would%20probably%20not%20have%20any%20global%20equivalent.%20His%20policies%20resulted%20in%20free%20ration%20to%20800%20million%20citizens%2C%20100%20million%20cooking%20gas%20connections%2C%20houses%20to%2040%20million%20poor%20families%20and%20190%20million%20tap%20water%20connections%20and%20counting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20critical%20aspect%20of%20his%20social%20transformation%20has%20been%20civic%20engagement%20and%20change%20in%20civic%20behaviour.%20An%20increase%20in%20gender%20ratio%20due%20to%20the%20Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%20campaign%20and%20the%20focus%20on%20cleanliness%20under%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%20are%20examples%20of%20how%20PM%20Modi%20has%20brought%20about%20lasting%20changes%20in%20Indian%20society.%20He%20has%20also%20empowered%20Indian%20women%20through%20transformational%20ideas%20like%20the%20abolition%20of%20Triple%20Talaq%20and%20innovative%20initiatives%20like%20Lakhpati%20Didis%20and%20Drone%20Didis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20wins%20because%20he%20embodies%20the%20aspirations%20of%20all%20Indians.%20He%20is%20personally%20and%20singularly%20invested%20in%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20lives%20of%20each%20and%20every%20Indian%20citizen.%20And%20voters%20repose%20faith%20in%20him%2C%20because%20he%20is%20believable%2C%20likeable%20and%20capable%20-%20a%20triumvirate%20of%20leadership%20abilities%20that%20is%20rare%20to%20find%20in%20public%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amit%20Malviya%20is%20in-charge%2C%20BJP%20National%20Information%20and%20Technology%20Department.%20He%20is%20also%20BJP's%20co-in-charge%20for%20Bengal)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717578960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F2c4h1tuo_pm-modi_625x300_01_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fon-pm-modi-winning-a-historic-mandate-5823128%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Make%20no%20mistake%20-%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20won%20a%20historic%20mandate.%20This%20is%20the%20third%20general%20election%20won%20under%20his%20leadership%20by%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fon-pm-modi-winning-a-historic-mandate-5823128%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20jailed%20candidates%20have%20won%20LS%20polls.%20Can%20they%20take%20oath%20and%20how%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717578715000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110730299%2Cimgsize-757240.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftwo-jailed-candidates-amritpal-singh-sheikh-abdul-rashid-have-won-lok-sabha-elections-can-they-take-oath-and-how%2Farticleshow%2F110730270.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20victory%20of%20two%20candidates%20who%20are%20in%20jail%20on%20terror%20charges%20has%20brought%20up%20a%20unique%20situation.%20While%20the%20law%20will%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20attending%20proceedings%20of%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20they%20also%20have%20a%20Constitutional%20right%20to%20take%20oath%20as%20members.%20In%20the%20results%20declared%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20jailed%20Sikh%20preacher%20Amritpal%20Singh%20has%20won%20from%20the%20Khadoor%20Sahib%20seat%2C%20while%20incarcerated%20Sheikh%20Abdul%20Rashid%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Engineer%20Rashid%2C%20emerged%20victorious%20from%20the%20Baramulla%20constituency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftwo-jailed-candidates-amritpal-singh-sheikh-abdul-rashid-have-won-lok-sabha-elections-can-they-take-oath-and-how%2Farticleshow%2F110730270.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20To%20Take%20Oath%20On%20Saturday%2C%20Submits%20Resignation%20To%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpm-modi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20take%20oath%20for%20a%20third%20time%20on%20Saturday%2C%20and%20in%20so%20doing%2C%20become%20the%20first%20(and%20only)%20three-term%20leader%20of%20the%20country%20since%20Congress%20stalwart%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjawaharlal-nehru%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJawaharlal%20Nehru%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mr%20Modi%20met%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20at%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20in%20Delhi%20to%20submit%20his%20resignation%2C%20and%20that%20of%20his%20cabinet.%20He%20was%20then%20requested%20to%20continue%20in%20his%20role%20till%20the%20swearing-in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi's%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20-%20which%20claimed%20282%20seats%20in%202014%20and%20303%20in%20the%202019%20election%20won%20240%20seats%20this%20time%20-%2032%20short%20of%20the%20272-majority%20mark.%20It%20will%20now%20rely%20on%20the%2053%20seats%20won%20by%20members%20of%20the%20party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20to%20seal%20a%20third%20term.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20retained%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Varanasi%2C%20defeating%20the%20Congress'%20Ajay%20Rai%20by%20less%20than%201.5%20lakh%20votes%20to%20become%20a%20three-time%20MP%20from%20the%20temple%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%20Mr%20Modi%20-%20who%20last%20evening%20confirmed%20the%20NDA%20would%20stake%20claim%20to%20form%20the%20government%20for%20a%20third%20time%2C%20calling%20the%20poll%20results%20a%20%26quot%3Bvictory%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%26quot%3B%20-%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20for%20the%20final%20time%20in%20this%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20set%20itself%20an%20ambitious%20target%20of%20370%20seats%20(400%2B%20including%20NDA%20partners)%2C%20but%20they%20were%20pegged%20back%20by%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20-%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc.%20The%20opposition%20has%20232%20seats%20after%20a%20stellar%20performance%20that%20saw%20it%20defy%20exit%20pollsters%20and%20slash%20the%20BJP's%20advantage%20in%20key%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20though%2C%20had%20enough%20in%20its%20tank%20to%20finish%20as%20the%20single-largest%20party%20yet%20again%2C%20thanks%20to%20good%20results%20from%20Odisha%20(20%20of%2021%20seats)%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(21%20of%2025)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(29%20of%2029)%2C%20and%20Bihar%20(30%20of%2040)%2C%20to%20offset%20the%20losses%20there%20and%20in%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20made%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20Kerala%20to%20win%20its%20first%20ever%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%20The%20BJP%20has%20historically%20struggled%20in%20the%20south%2C%20but%20the%20Kerala%20and%20Andhra%20results%2C%20as%20well%20as%20doubling%20its%20Telangana%20tally%20to%20eight%2C%20suggest%20a%20change.%20The%20party%20did%2C%20however%2C%20finish%20with%20zero%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%20a%20second%20consecutive%20election.%20The%20ruling%20DMK%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20allies%20won%20all%2039%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpeople-have-trusted-nda-for-third-time-historic-moment-pm-modi-on-election-results-5816999%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20Trusted%20NDA%20For%20Third%20Time%2C%20Historic%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20On%20Election%20Results%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20addressing%20an%20adoring%20crowd%20at%20the%20party's%20Delhi%20HQ%20late%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20people%20of%20India%20had%20%26quot%3Bplaced%20their%20faith%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20NDA%20for%20a%20third%20time.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20bow%20to%20the%20people%20for%20this%20affection%20and%20assure%20them%20we%20will%20continue%20the%20good%20work%20done%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20to%20keep%20fulfilling%20aspirations..%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20also%20made%20special%20mention%20of%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20leader%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20boss%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20veteran%2C%20coalition-era%20politicians%20who%20are%20now%20seen%20as%20kingmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERE