le%20in%20the%20NDA%20until%202004.%20He%20returned%20to%20the%20NDA%20in%202014%2C%20won%20a%20bifurcated%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20left%20it%20in%202018.%20He%20lost%20power%20and%20rejoined%20the%20NDA%20after%20he%20was%20jailed%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20by%20the%20YSRCP%20government.%20The%20BJP%20drove%20a%20tough%20bargain%2C%20made%20him%20wait%20and%20eventually%20finalised%20a%20deal%2C%20extracting%20its%20pound%20of%20flesh%20in%20terms%20of%20seats%20-%20it%20snagged%20six%20of%20the%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Andhra%20despite%20its%20negligible%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20during%20the%202014%20election%20campaign%2C%20the%20TDP%20even%20insisted%20that%20NaMo%20stands%20for%20Naidu%20and%20Modi%20(instead%20of%20Narendra%20Modi).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20will%20extract%20his%20pound%20of%20flesh%20from%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20a%20most%20strategic%20negotiator%2C%20patient%20and%20calibrated.%20Given%20the%20numbers%20-%20around%20238%20seats%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20single%20largest%20party%2C%20and%20100%20for%20runner-up%20Congress%20-%20it%20would%20seem%20difficult%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20cobble%20numbers.%20Even%20if%20it%20does%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20highly%20unstable%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20this%2C%20but%20keeping%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20option%20in%20play%20only%20increases%20his%20bargaining%20power%20with%20the%20NDA.%20And%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20drive%20a%20very%20tough%20bargain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20status%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20is%20already%20a%20major%20demand%2C%20but%20Naidu%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20focus%20on%20sustained%20economic%20benefits%20for%20his%20state.%20He%20was%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Hyderabad%20IT%20dream%2C%20but%20it%20was%20cut%20short%20by%20a%20series%20of%20political%20disasters.%20First%2C%20the%20successive%20losses%20in%202004%20and%202009%2C%20and%20then%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201999%2C%20Naidu%20stayed%20out%20of%20the%20cabinet%20and%20ensured%20the%20TDP%20got%20the%20Speaker's%20post%20in%20parliament.%20He%20may%20follow%20a%20similar%20strategy%20this%20time%2C%20which%20will%20put%20Modi's%20negotiating%20skills%20to%20test.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20never%20led%20a%20coalition%20and%20negotiating%20with%20Naidu%20could%20be%20a%20challenge.%20Over%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20Vajpayee-era%20coalition%20builders%2C%20and%20for%20the%20hard%20and%20aggressive%20new%20lot%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20skill%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20numbers%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20a%20pre-poll%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20Naidu%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20NDA.%20Coalition%20politics%2C%20however%2C%20is%20an%20uncertain%20beast%20and%20it%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20watch%20how%20the%20line%20between%20Vijayawada%20and%20Delhi%20evolves%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days%20and%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%2C%20too%2C%20is%20a%20veteran%20of%20coalition%20politics%20and%20had%20a%20stint%20in%20the%20NDA%20cabinet%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20until%20he%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20in%202004.%20He%20has%20played%20all%20sides%20and%20has%20switched%20alliances%20with%20ease.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20original%20architects%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20but%20walked%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20months%20before%20polls.%20He%2C%20too%2C%20will%20demand%20his%20pound%20of%20flesh%2C%20but%20he%20is%20a%20coalition%20partner%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20as%20well%20and%20may%20not%20want%20to%20upset%20the%20apple%20cart%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20ultimate%20dream%20is%20the%20PM's%20post%20and%20if%20that%20is%20on%20the%20table%2C%20he%20could%20go%20anywhere.%20That%20is%20a%20long%20shot%20with%20just%2014%20seats.%20For%20now%2C%20he%20could%20leverage%20his%20numbers%20for%20cabinet%20berths%20as%20well%20as%20finances%20for%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717576440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftimhnrgg_nitish-kumar-chandrababu-naidu-_625x300_05_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-post-verdict-2024-delhi-needs-to-learn-the-art-of-negotiating-5822761%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20Vijayawada%20and%20Patna%20may%20play%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20the%20power%20equations%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Chief%20Minister-in-waiting%2C%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20both%20are%20veterans%20of%20coalition%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-post-verdict-2024-delhi-needs-to-learn-the-art-of-negotiating-5822761%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ajay%20Devgn%20wraps%20shoot%20for%20Raid%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717576357000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110728627%2Cimgsize-30910.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fajay-devgn-wraps-shoot-for-raid-2-directed-by-raj-kumar-gupta-reports%2Farticleshow%2F110728460.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110728460.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECurrently%20immersed%20in%20post-production%2C%20Devgn%20portrays%20Amay%20Patnaik%2C%20a%20senior%20income%20tax%20official%2C%20in%20'Raid%202.'On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Devgn'%20recent%20sports%20drama%2C%20'Maidaan%2C'%20depicting%20the%20life%20of%20legendary%20Indian%20football%20coach%20Syed%20Abdul%20Rahim%2C%20has%20made%20its%20way%20to%20streaming%20platforms%20after%20its%20theatrical%20release%20in%20April%20this%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fajay-devgn-wraps-shoot-for-raid-2-directed-by-raj-kumar-gupta-reports%2Farticleshow%2F110728460.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%20Decoding%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20And%20BJD's%20Shock%20Odisha%20Defeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAlthough%20born%20in%20Odisha's%20Cuttack%2C%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20lived%20most%20of%20his%20life%20in%20a%20sprawling%20family%20estate%20in%20Lutyens'%20Delhi.%20The%20premium%20estate%2C%20located%20between%20Prithviraj%20Road%20and%20Aurangzeb%20Road%2C%20was%20bought%20by%20his%20father%20Biju%20Patnaik%20from%20the%20Maharaja%20of%20Jubbal%2C%20and%20once%20hosted%20global%20icons%20like%20Mick%20Jagger%2C%20Robert%20De%20Nero%2C%20Jackie%20Kennedy%20and%20Bruce%20Chatwin.%20Long%20before%20Mr%20Patnaik%20emerged%20as%20a%20political%20stalwart%2C%20this%20house%20was%20a%20sanctuary%20for%20the%20elite%20and%20the%20artistic%20of%20Delhi's%20socialite%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20father's%20death%20in%201997%2C%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20relinquished%20the%20haute%20monde%20of%20the%20nation's%20capital%2C%20returned%20to%20Odisha%20and%20ruled%20as%20its%20chief%20minister%20for%20over%2024%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%202024%2C%20and%20an%20unprecedented%20jolt%20for%20Naveen%20Babu%2C%20once%20considered%20invincible.%20The%20BJP%20ended%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)'s%20reign%20by%20not%20only%20securing%2078%20of%20the%20state's%20147%20assembly%20seats%20but%20also%20claiming%2020%20out%20of%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20With%20just%2051%20assembly%20seats%20and%20a%20complete%20wipeout%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJD%20is%20reeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20results%20mean%20Mr%20Patnaik%20fell%2073%20days%20short%20of%20eclipsing%20Pawan%20Chamling%20as%20the%20longest-serving%20chief%20minister%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20seismic%20shift%20has%20left%20many%20wondering%20-%20what%20caused%20this%20political%20titan%20to%20tumble%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%26quot%3BOutsider%20Sentiment%26quot%3B%20And%20VK%20Pandian%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20foremost%20reasons%20for%20the%20BJD's%20downfall%20was%20the%20growing%20anti-outsider%20sentiment%2C%20particularly%20aimed%20at%20VK%20Pandian%2C%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20trusted%20aide%20and%20private%20secretary.%20Mr%20Pandian%2C%20a%20former%20IAS%20officer%2C%20wielded%20immense%20influence%20within%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20state's%20administrative%20machinery%2C%20often%20seen%20as%20the%20de%20facto%20ruler.%20This%20perception%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Boutsider%26quot%3B%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20running%20the%20government%20did%20not%20sit%20well%20with%20the%20Odia%20populace%2C%20who%20began%20to%20resent%20Mr%20Pandian's%20dominance%20and%20his%20style%20of%20functioning.%20The%20BJP%20capitalised%20on%20this%20sentiment%2C%20portraying%20the%20BJD%20as%20being%20puppeteered%20by%20an%20unelected%20bureaucrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Modi-Shah%20Factor%20And%20Odia%20%3Cem%3EAsmita%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20campaign%20was%20marked%20by%20an%20aggressive%20focus%20on%20Odia%20%3Cem%3EAsmita%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20Odia%20self-identity.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20spearheaded%20an%20exhaustive%20campaign%2C%20stressing%20Odisha's%20pride%20and%20urging%20voters%20to%20reclaim%20their%20state%20from%20a%20regime%20they%20painted%20as%20distant%20and%20disconnected.%20PM%20Modi's%2010%20rallies%20and%20roadshows%2C%20coupled%20with%20Mr%20Shah's%20robust%20campaign%20trail%2C%20resonated%20deeply%20with%20voters%2C%20especially%20in%20regions%20where%20the%20BJD%20had%20historically%20been%20dominant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaveen%20Patnaik's%20Diminished%20Visibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20critical%20factor%20was%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20conspicuous%20absence%20from%20the%20campaign%20trail.%20Unlike%20previous%20elections%2C%20where%20his%20presence%20was%20ubiquitous%2C%20this%20time%20Mr%20Patnaik%20was%20less%20visible.%20In%20the%20rallies%20where%20he%20actually%20turned%20up%2C%20he%20was%20always%20accompanied%20by%20the%20omnipresent%20Mr%20Pandian%2C%20who%20either%20held%20a%20mic%20for%20the%2077-year-old%2C%20or%20kept%20his%20hand%20steady%2C%20or%20shadowed%20Mr%20Patnaik%20as%20he%20waved%20to%20party%20workers.%20This%20void%20left%20the%20BJD's%20campaign%20lacklustre%20and%20less%20compelling.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP's%20carpet-bombing%20saw%2C%20besides%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20leaders%20like%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20and%20Hema%20Malini%20adding%20star%20power%20that%20the%20BJD%20sorely%20lacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETactical%20Missteps%20And%20Lack%20of%20Succession%20Planning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD's%20strategy%20of%20providing%20tacit%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20national%20level%20backfired%20spectacularly.%20This%20cozy%20arrangement%20had%20initially%20helped%20the%20BJD%20but%20eventually%20blurred%20the%20lines%20between%20ally%20and%20opponent%2C%20eroding%20BJD's%20distinct%20identity.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20BJD's%20glaring%20lack%20of%20a%20succession%20plan%20became%20a%20critical%20Achilles'%20heel.%20As%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20health%20became%20a%20focal%20point%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20clear%20heir%20apparent%20created%20uncertainty%20and%20diminished%20confidence%20among%20the%20electorate.%20Rumours%20and%20speculation%20about%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20health%20further%20fueled%20the%20BJP's%20narrative%2C%20with%20PM%20Modi%20even%20hinting%20at%20possible%20conspiracies%20behind%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20declining%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDharmendra%20Pradhan's%20Western%20Odisha%20Campaign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20strategic%20focus%20on%20Western%20Odisha%2C%20an%20area%20often%20perceived%20as%20neglected%2C%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20their%20victory.%20Mr%20Pradhan%2C%20a%20Union%20Minister%2C%20camped%20in%20Sambalpur%20and%20vigorously%20campaigned%20with%20promises%20of%20upliftment%20and%20development%20for%20the%20region.%20His%20stature%20as%20a%20national%20leader%20provided%20voters%20a%20compelling%20alternative%20to%20Mr%20Patnaik%2C%20who%20clearly%20lacked%20an%20heir%20that%20would%20be%20accepted%20by%20everyone%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOverconfidence%20And%20The%20%26quot%3B400%20Paar%26quot%3B%20Parallel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD's%20claims%20throughout%20the%20campaigning%20period%20that%20Mr%20Patnaik%20would%20comfortably%20secure%20a%20sixth%20term%20mirrored%20the%20NDA's%20%26quot%3B400%20paar%26quot%3B%20claim%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20complacency%20within%20the%20BJD.%20This%20overconfidence%20was%20starkly%20evident%20in%20their%20campaign%20strategy%2C%20which%20lacked%20the%20urgency%20and%20rigour%20seen%20in%20previous%20elections.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP's%20relentless%20and%20energised%20campaign%20capitalised%20on%20this%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20decisive%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ratnabhandar%20Controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ratnabhandar%20issue%2C%20revolving%20around%20the%20missing%20key%20of%20Lord%20Jagannath's%20treasury%2C%20was%20another%20significant%20blow%20to%20the%20BJD.%20The%20BJP%20adeptly%20exploited%20this%20controversy%2C%20pitching%20it%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20BJD's%20mismanagement%20and%20lack%20of%20respect%20for%20Odia%20cultural%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717576200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fimqdlfo_naveen-patnaik-_625x300_05_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-results-odisha-elections-analysis-decoding-naveen-patnaik-and-bjds-shock-odisha-defeat-5822840%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20his%20father's%20death%20in%201997%2C%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20relinquished%20the%20haute%20monde%20of%20the%20nation's%20capital%2C%20returned%20to%20Odisha%20and%20ruled%20as%20its%20chief%20minister%20for%20over%2024%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-results-odisha-elections-analysis-decoding-naveen-patnaik-and-bjds-shock-odisha-defeat-5822840%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-results-odisha-elections-analysis-decoding-naveen-patnaik-and-bjds-shock-odisha-defeat-5822840%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-results-odisha-elections-analysis-decoding-naveen-patnaik-and-bjds-shock-odisha-defeat-5822840%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SpiceJet%20aims%20to%20raise%20%24250%20mn%20in%20coming%20months%2C%20says%20CEO%20Ajay%20Singh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717575909000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-03%2F20%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1679331030-0807.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fspicejet-aims-to-raise-250-mn-in-coming-months-says-ceo-ajay-singh-124060500433_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20airline%20is%20tackling%20multiple%20headwinds%2C%20including%20lessor%20and%20debt%20woes%2C%20with%20Singh%20saying%20the%20carrier%20has%20faced%20%