oolers%20in%20their%20kirana%20stores%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352124%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Pathak%20(L)%20and%20Anil%20Prasad%20(R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20India%2C%20approximately%2020%20percent%20of%20a%20retailer%E2%80%99s%20income%20is%20generated%20from%20beverage%20sales%2C%20with%206%C2%A0%20percent%20specifically%20attributed%20to%20the%20sale%20of%20Coca-Cola%20beverages.%20The%20introduction%20of%20coolers%20has%20ramped%20up%20sales%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%20India%E2%80%99s%20Superpower%20Retailer%20Program%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20transformation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20three-year%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSDC)%20under%20the%20Skill%20India%20Mission%2C%20focusing%20on%20empowering%20small%20retailers%20in%20the%20states%20of%20Odisha%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%20more%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20empowers%20retailers%20by%20building%20their%20capacity%20and%20capability%20in%20modern%20retailing%20and%20provides%20training%20to%20small%20and%20micro%20retailers%2C%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20needed%20to%20better%20understand%20consumer%20behaviours%20and%20preferences.%20Amanpreet%2C%