%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdil-dhadakne-do-turns-9-here-is-what-aamir-khan-said-about-voicing-the-dog-pluto-in-the-zoya-akhtar-directorial%2Farticleshow%2F110727324.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCar%20Is%20Sent%203%20Hours%20Away%20For%20A%20Burger%26quot%3B%3A%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20On%20Stars'%20Demands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fimtiaz-ali-to-anurag-kashyap-can-you-name-all-the-directors-in-zoya-akhtars-throwback-pic-5785254%5C%22%3EDirector%20Anurag%20Kashyap%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20budget%20and%20the%20revenue%20of%20films.%20Talking%20about%20how%20a%20film's%20budget%20is%20spent%20on%20%E2%80%9Cparaphernalia%E2%80%9D%2C%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20told%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-a8C3kZbxyo%5C%22%3EHumans%20of%20Cinema%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20spending%20the%20money%20on%20the%20film.%20People%20need%20to%20come%20back%20to%20this%20whole%20reality%20check.%20One%20thing%20people%20need%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20when%20we%20make%20a%20film%2C%20we're%20working%2C%20we're%20creating%20something.%20It's%20not%20a%20holiday%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20picnic.%20A%20lot%20of%20money%20that%20is%20spent%20doesn't%20go%20into%20making%20the%20film.%20It%20goes%20into%20the%20paraphernalia%3B%20it%20goes%20into%20the%20entourage.%20You're%20shooting%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20jungle%2C%20but%20one%20car%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20city%20three%20hours%20away%20specifically%20to%20get%20you%20that%20five-star%20burger%20you%20want.%20You%20don't%20get%20into%20the%20process%20of%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmaharaja-trailer-vijay-sethupathi-and-anurag-kashyap-in-a-revenge-saga-5783835%5C%22%3EAnurag%20Kashyap%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20said%20that%20independent%20ideas%20are%20not%20getting%20the%20backing.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20mainstream%2C%20independent%20ideas%20work%20much%20more.%20But%20the%20thing%20is%20they%20don't%20get%20the%20backing.%20Today%20you%20go%20to%20any%20actor%2C%20any%20star.%20They%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20whether%20it%20(the%20project)%20is%20a%20big%20project%20or%20not%2C%20whether%20it%20will%20be%20hit%20or%20not%2C%20whether%20it%20will%20make%20business%20or%20not.%20They%20think%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20script%20is%20good%20but%20what%20can%20we%20do%20so%20that%20it%20earns%20more'.%20If%20the%20script%20is%20good%2C%20they%20must%20do%20it.%20Everybody%20starts%20thinking%20of%20what%20will%20happen%20after%20the%20film%20comes%20out.%20But%20nobody%20is%20going%20by%20instinct.%20We%20all%20are%20very%20caught%20up%20in%20this.%20And%20social%20media%20is%20the%20biggest%20culprit%20in%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-breaks-silence-on-rift-with-filmmaker-anurag-kashyap-5727731%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGangs%20of%20Wasseypur%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0director%3C%2Fa%3E%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20film's%20business%20has%20taken%20over%20everyone.%20Everybody%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20box%20office%20numbers.%20And%20in%20a%20time%20like%20today%20when%20people%20are%20actually%20making%20much%20more%20money%20than%20they%20would%20have%2020%20years%20ago%20they%20feel%20short-changed.%20When%20I%20was%20working%20as%20a%20writer%2C%20my%20fees%20for%20the%20entire%20film%20were%20less%20than%20what%20a%20first%20AD%20would%20get%20per%20month%20today.%20But%20I%20cannot%20make%20a%20film%20today%20like%20I%20made%C2%A0%3Cem%3EGulaal%2C%20Raman%20Raghav%202.0%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EUgly%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20because%20of%20politics%20as%20well%20as%20budgeting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Kashyap%20also%20shared%20an%20instance%20from%20his%202018%20series%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESacred%20Games.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20budget%20the%20film%20at%20that%20cost%2C%20today%2C%20because%20when%20OTTs%20came%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20got%20spoiled.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20so%20many%20vanity%20vans%20on%20my%20set%20as%20I%20had%20seen%20on%20Sacred%20Games.%20That's%20how%20the%20culture%20got%20started.%20Then%20you%20can't%20reverse%20that.%20Finally%2C%20those%20people%20started%20getting%20paid%20who%20were%20totally%20ignored%2C%20which%20is%20the%20technical%20crew%2C%20who%20work%20the%20longest%20on%20a%20film.%20They%20come%20in%20first%2C%20they%20leave%20last.%20The%20actor%20comes%2C%20shoots%20and%20goes.%20But%20people%20who%20were%20least%20paid%20started%20getting%20paid%2C%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20fair%20way.%20But%20a%20lot%20of%20extra%20things%20started%20coming%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20you%20cannot%20go%20from%20there.%20The%20reversing%20will%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20gaps%20now.%20It%20will%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%20Actors%20have%20to%20revise%20their%20prices.%20Now%2C%20OTTs%20have%20also%20realised%20this.%20Everyone%20wants%20to%20cut%20down%20costs%20now.%20What%20has%20happened%20is%2C%20initially%20everyone%20raised%20the%20cost%2C%20but%20now%20they%20want%20to%20cut%20it%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717573320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fsj477mog_anurag_625x300_05_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fanurag-kashyap-opens-up-on-budget-and-revenue-of-films-in-today-s-world-5822259%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20money%20that%20is%20spent%20doesn't%20go%20into%20making%20the%20film.%20It%20goes%20into%20the%20paraphernalia%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anurag%20Kashyap%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fan