ic%20material.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSafety%2Fstatus%2F1797669613775282677%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20X%20announced%20the%20launch%20of%20updated%20policies%20regarding%20%E2%80%9CAdult%20Content%20and%20Violent%20Content%E2%80%9D%20on%20its%20platform.%20These%20new%20policies%20aim%20to%20provide%20greater%20%E2%80%9Cclarity%E2%80%9D%20regarding%20the%20rules%20governing%20such%20content%20and%20increase%20%E2%80%9Ctransparency%20in%20their%20enforcement%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThese%20policies%20replace%20the%20%E2%80%9Cformer%20Sensitive%20Media%20and%20Violent%20Speech%20policies%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20said%2C%20even%20though%20the%20underlying%20principles%20of%20enforcement%20remain%20unchanged.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnX's%20policy%20also%20extends%20to%20AI-generated%20and%20animated%20content.%20The%20platform%20permits%20adult%20nudity%20or%20sexual%20content%2C%20including%20AI-generated%2C%20photographic%2C%20or%20animated%20projections.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EWhat%20X%20means%20by%20%E2%80%98Adult'%20and%20%E2%80%98Violent'%20content%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThey%20clarified%20that%20%E2%80%9CAdult%20Content%20covers%20our%20approach%20to%20sharing%20consensual%20sexual%20content%20and%20adult%20nudity%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CViolent%20Content%20covers%20violent%20speech%20and%20violent%20media%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20more%20holistic%20approach%20to%20combating%20violence%20in%20all%20forms.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BAdult%20content%26quot%3B%20will%20show%20full%20or%20partial%20nudity%2C%20including%20close-ups%20of%20genitals%2C%20buttocks%20or%20breasts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20explicit%20or%20implied%20sexual%20behaviour%20or%20simulated%20acts%20like%20sexual%20intercourse.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EHow%20to%20mark%20content%20on%20X%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20users%20who%20frequently%20share%20adult%20content%20on%20X%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.x.com%2Fen%2Frules-and-policies%2Fadult-content%C2%A0%5C%22%3Eplatform%20suggests%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadjusting%20their%20media%20settings%20accordingly.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20will%20ensure%20such%20images%20and%20videos%20are%20placed%20behind%20a%20content%20warning%2C%20which%20pops%20up%20before%20they%20are%20viewed.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20option%20to%20add%20a%20one-time%20content%20warning%20to%20individual%20posts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnX%20also%20said%20that%20if%20anyone%20doesn't%20mark%20their%20posts%20correctly%2C%20the%20platform%20will%20do%20it%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EHarmful%20content%20will%20be%20prohibited%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20platform%20will%20continue%20to%20ban%20pornographic%20content%20that%20is%20harmful%20or%20non-consensual%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20material%20that%20promotes%20the%20objectification%20of%20people%20or%20harm%20to%20minors.%20Moreover%2C%20adult%20content%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20in%20profile%20pictures%2C%20banners%20or%20other%20publicly%20visible%20areas.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EHow%20to%20report%20content%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20report%20unmarked%20content%20or%20any%20other%20violations%2C%20use%20the%20%E2%80%98report'%20option%20on%20the%20app.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EPolicy%20for%20underage%20users%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20policy%2C%20users%20under%2018%20or%20those%20who%20haven't%20provided%20their%20birth%20date%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20view%20posts%20marked%20as%20adult%20content.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20decision%2C%20announced%20on%20Monday%2C%20marks%20a%20significant%20change%20in%20what%20is%20permissible%20on%20the%20platform%20and%20arrives%20amid%20pressure%20to%20protect%20children%20from%20looking%20at%20inappropriate%20content%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717569600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https