another%20shop%20in%20Nellore.%20Within%20three%20years%2C%20I%20have%20established%20more%20than%2015%20stores%20across%20South%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20quick%20to%20get%20into%20the%20B2B%20business%20of%20franchising%20his%20icecream%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20the%20company%20makes%20six%20to%20seven%20lakh%20litres%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345217%2Fbest-ice-cream-parlours-places-mumbai-snowman-taj-icecream-haji-ali-gokul-rustom-naturals-bachelorr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eicecream%20every%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESwitch%20to%20organic%20icecreams%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Suhas%20was%20making%20good%20profits%2C%20the%20work%20began%20to%20feel%20monotonous.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20reinvesting%20all%20the%20earnings%20from%20my%20business%20back%20into%20the%20same%20model.%20However%2C%20I%20soon%20realised%20that%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20direction%20I%20wanted%20for%20my%20business.%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20more%3B%20a%20satisfaction%20that%20I%20was%20doing%20something%20good.%20I%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20food%20business%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20sustainable%20and%20organic%20living%20was%20being%20circulated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20realised%20that%20it%20might%20be%20the%20right%20time%20to%20switch%20and%20give%20people%20an%20alternative%20to%20regular%20icecreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%20target%20the%20market%20for%20organic%20icecreams%3F%E2%80%99%20Considering%20the%20popularity%20of%20organic%20products%20like%20biscuits%2C%20%3Cem%3Enamkeen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20even%20%3Cem%3Eagarbatti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I